{
  "video_id": "nUv8zsthlUU",
  "title": "How to block spam calls",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 282.0,
      "end_time": 2277.0,
      "text": "Spam calls are worse than ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2277.0,
      "end_time": 4632.0,
      "text": "That's not just my opinion, it's not just how we all feel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4632.0,
      "end_time": 5465.0,
      "text": "it's true."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 5849.0,
      "end_time": 7873.0,
      "text": "Robocall complaints to the federal trade commission"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 7873.0,
      "end_time": 9938.0,
      "text": "have quintupled since 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 9938.0,
      "end_time": 12625.0,
      "text": "and they jumped steeply in just the past year to four and a half million total."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15115.0,
      "end_time": 16643.0,
      "text": "And that's just Robocalls."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16643.0,
      "end_time": 18580.0,
      "text": "There are another two and a half million complaints"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 18580.0,
      "end_time": 19901.0,
      "text": "about live telemarketers."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19901.0,
      "end_time": 21742.0,
      "text": "So what on earth can we do to start fighting back"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 21742.0,
      "end_time": 23510.0,
      "text": "against all these spammy calls?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 23510.0,
      "end_time": 25155.0,
      "text": "There are three steps you can take,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 25155.0,
      "end_time": 26867.0,
      "text": "they won't solve the problem entirely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 26867.0,
      "end_time": 27400.0,
      "text": "but if you're fed up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 27400.0,
      "end_time": 30362.0,
      "text": "this is what you can do to start fighting back."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 30362.0,
      "end_time": 32779.0,
      "text": "HOW TO BLOCK SPAM CALLS"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 32973.0,
      "end_time": 34162.0,
      "text": "Okay so, step number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 34162.0,
      "end_time": 35350.0,
      "text": "Use a call-blocking app,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 35350.0,
      "end_time": 36478.0,
      "text": "there are a whole bunch of these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 36478.0,
      "end_time": 37769.0,
      "text": "and they all try to do the same thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 37769.0,
      "end_time": 40802.0,
      "text": "block spam calls before you have to answer your phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 40802.0,
      "end_time": 43447.0,
      "text": "Some of the most popular include Hiya and Truecaller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 43447.0,
      "end_time": 44289.0,
      "text": "which are free."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 44289.0,
      "end_time": 47325.0,
      "text": "And Nomorobo and RoboKiller, which require a subscription."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 47325.0,
      "end_time": 48442.0,
      "text": "We're gonna use Nomorobo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 48442.0,
      "end_time": 51275.0,
      "text": "because it won the FTC's Robocall Blocking Challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 51275.0,
      "end_time": 52839.0,
      "text": "But these all work more or less the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 52839.0,
      "end_time": 54929.0,
      "text": "and they work for both iOS and Android."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 54929.0,
      "end_time": 56634.0,
      "text": "Once you've installed it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 56634.0,
      "end_time": 58521.0,
      "text": "you'll have to get the app permission to handle your Caller ID."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 58521.0,
      "end_time": 59598.0,
      "text": "They also have a huge"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 59598.0,
      "end_time": 62376.0,
      "text": "constantly updating list of known spammers."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 62376.0,
      "end_time": 65313.0,
      "text": "And it check those numbers against who's calling you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 65313.0,
      "end_time": 67323.0,
      "text": "if it sees that a known spammer is calling you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 67323.0,
      "end_time": 68630.0,
      "text": "it either won't let the number through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 68630.0,
      "end_time": 70765.0,
      "text": "or it'll identify you when they're calling."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 70766.0,
      "end_time": 72776.0,
      "text": "If the app does let a spam call through by accident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 72776.0,
      "end_time": 74118.0,
      "text": "then you can tell it that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 74118.0,
      "end_time": 76541.0,
      "text": "and it will then factor that information in for everybody else"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 76541.0,
      "end_time": 78262.0,
      "text": "to help blocking(block) more spam calls."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 78263.0,
      "end_time": 79448.0,
      "text": "Since most of these apps are free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 79447.0,
      "end_time": 80731.0,
      "text": "there's no harm in just trying one out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 80731.0,
      "end_time": 81899.0,
      "text": "to see how it works for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 81899.0,
      "end_time": 83384.0,
      "text": "But before we go any further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 83384.0,
      "end_time": 86824.0,
      "text": "what's behind all these spam calls anyway?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 86824.0,
      "end_time": 88963.0,
      "text": "Since our private numbers are basically everywhere now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 88963.0,
      "end_time": 90384.0,
      "text": "mainly on our online accounts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 90385.0,
      "end_time": 91934.0,
      "text": "pasted at our email signatures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 91934.0,
      "end_time": 93419.0,
      "text": "and printed on business cards."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 93419.0,
      "end_time": 95934.0,
      "text": "In giving our phone numbers to pretty much everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 95934.0,
      "end_time": 97770.0,
      "text": "there's a good chance they will be shuffled along"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 97770.0,
      "end_time": 99342.0,
      "text": "to someone they shouldn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 99342.0,
      "end_time": 102234.0,
      "text": "Plus, thanks to auto-dialing software and the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 102234.0,
      "end_time": 105121.0,
      "text": "scammers can place thousands of calls a min,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 105121.0,
      "end_time": 106538.0,
      "text": "for really cheap."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 106682.0,
      "end_time": 108986.0,
      "text": "They can even guess out numbers if they want to."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 108986.0,
      "end_time": 110165.0,
      "text": "And once they're dialed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 110165.0,
      "end_time": 112762.0,
      "text": "the auto-dialer can then play back a pre-recorded message,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 112762.0,
      "end_time": 114474.0,
      "text": "when someone would talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 114474.0,
      "end_time": 117430.0,
      "text": "Technology is also making spammers more clever."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 117430.0,
      "end_time": 118668.0,
      "text": "Letting them disguise their phone number"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 118668.0,
      "end_time": 121179.0,
      "text": "as a local one with your own area code."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 121179.0,
      "end_time": 123179.0,
      "text": "That way, you're more likely to answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 123179.0,
      "end_time": 126241.0,
      "text": "giving each fake call, a better chance of landing."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 126241.0,
      "end_time": 128723.0,
      "text": "But why do we receive so many spam calls?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 128723.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130185.00000000001,
      "text": "Well, as you can guess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 130185.0,
      "end_time": 132441.0,
      "text": "someone is profiting from this."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 132441.0,
      "end_time": 134191.0,
      "text": "The caller ID company Truecaller"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 134191.0,
      "end_time": 138774.0,
      "text": "estimates that phone scammers made 9.5 Billion in 2016,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 139140.0,
      "end_time": 140890.0,
      "text": "from Americans alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 141900.0,
      "end_time": 142545.0,
      "text": "And the more calls they send out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 142545.0,
      "end_time": 145607.0,
      "text": "the more chances they have finding(found) a target."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 145608.0,
      "end_time": 147673.0,
      "text": "And while this is a huge problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 147673.0,
      "end_time": 150748.0,
      "text": "it's actually really hard to crack down on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 150748.0,
      "end_time": 152415.0,
      "text": "Making spammy calls like these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 152415.0,
      "end_time": 154915.0,
      "text": "are largely illegal in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 154977.0,
      "end_time": 157395.0,
      "text": "But Robocalls can be placed from overseas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 157395.0,
      "end_time": 160970.0,
      "text": "and there's not much that the United States can do about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 160970.0,
      "end_time": 162588.0,
      "text": "And for phone service providers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 162588.0,
      "end_time": 165384.0,
      "text": "it can be hard to tell whether a call that's coming in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 165384.0,
      "end_time": 167570.0,
      "text": "is from a scammer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 167570.0,
      "end_time": 169226.0,
      "text": "or from someone you actually wanna get in touch with."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 169227.0,
      "end_time": 171689.0,
      "text": "They have to be careful not to block any calls"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 171689.0,
      "end_time": 173984.0,
      "text": "that really should have been let through."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 173985.0,
      "end_time": 177709.0,
      "text": "And it's important to know that some Robocalls are legal."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 177709.0,
      "end_time": 179326.0,
      "text": "Your pharmacy might call you."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 179326.0,
      "end_time": 181460.0,
      "text": "[Phone] Your prescription is ready."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 181460.0,
      "end_time": 182452.0,
      "text": "Or your child's school."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 182452.0,
      "end_time": 184897.0,
      "text": "- [Phone] We're closed due to inclement weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 184897.0,
      "end_time": 185769.0,
      "text": "Or even an airline."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 185770.0,
      "end_time": 187163.0,
      "text": "- [Phone] Your gate has changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 187163.0,
      "end_time": 189633.0,
      "text": "Generally speaking, these are all legal."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 189633.0,
      "end_time": 192469.0,
      "text": "The focus is on those calls from scammers."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 192469.0,
      "end_time": 193745.0,
      "text": "Claiming you won a free cruise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 193746.0,
      "end_time": 195675.0,
      "text": "or they can lower your interest rate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 195675.0,
      "end_time": 197913.0,
      "text": "or that the FBI is looking for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 197913.0,
      "end_time": 201546.0,
      "text": "The service Youmail estimates that 30% to 40%"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 201546.0,
      "end_time": 203720.0,
      "text": "of all Robocalls are scams."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 203720.0,
      "end_time": 206502.0,
      "text": "And you definitely shouldn't be receiving those calls."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 206502.0,
      "end_time": 208564.0,
      "text": "Alright, so what else can you do to stop spam calls?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 208564.0,
      "end_time": 210329.0,
      "text": "Well, there are a few other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 210330.0,
      "end_time": 213377.0,
      "text": "First, make sure your number is on the National Do Not Call Registry"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 213377.0,
      "end_time": 215580.0,
      "text": "if you're in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 215580.0,
      "end_time": 216912.0,
      "text": "Assuming those calls were coming in legally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 216913.0,
      "end_time": 219267.0,
      "text": "that could start to come down on some of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 219267.0,
      "end_time": 221239.0,
      "text": "Second, see what your phone provider can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 221239.0,
      "end_time": 223500.0,
      "text": "AT&T and T-Mobile both offer services"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 223500.0,
      "end_time": 226900.0,
      "text": "that are designed to identify spammy callers when they hit your phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 226901.0,
      "end_time": 228768.0,
      "text": "Verizon and Sprint have similar services,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 228768.0,
      "end_time": 230310.0,
      "text": "but they all charge for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 230310.0,
      "end_time": 232450.0,
      "text": "And finally, know what is it you do"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 232450.0,
      "end_time": 233150.0,
      "text": "when you get a spam call."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 233151.0,
      "end_time": 234754.0,
      "text": "Don't talk. Don't press any buttons."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 234754.0,
      "end_time": 236474.0,
      "text": "Don't let them know that a human is on the line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 236474.0,
      "end_time": 238796.0,
      "text": "or they might be likely to call back."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 238796.0,
      "end_time": 240000.0,
      "text": "Also, be aware of"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 240000.0,
      "end_time": 241685.0,
      "text": "what some of the most common phone scams are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 241685.0,
      "end_time": 243000.0,
      "text": "like free travel packages."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 243000.0,
      "end_time": 244741.0,
      "text": "So you don't give them your time or money."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 244741.0,
      "end_time": 246210.0,
      "text": "If you really do wanna talk to somebody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 246210.0,
      "end_time": 247590.0,
      "text": "consider calling them back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 247590.0,
      "end_time": 250540.0,
      "text": "from a number that you know is legitimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 250540.0,
      "end_time": 252000.0,
      "text": "Also, and this is really important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 252000.0,
      "end_time": 254287.0,
      "text": "when you're handing out your information over the phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 254287.0,
      "end_time": 256391.0,
      "text": "make sure you're really identifying yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 256391.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258000.00000000003,
      "text": "rather than handing your identity to somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 258000.0,
      "end_time": 259848.0,
      "text": "who doesn't already have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 259848.0,
      "end_time": 261663.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it might never be possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 261663.0,
      "end_time": 263497.0,
      "text": "to fully put a stop to Robocalls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 263497.0,
      "end_time": 265303.0,
      "text": "but you're not defenseless against them."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 265303.0,
      "end_time": 266641.0,
      "text": "The government and phone carriers"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 266641.0,
      "end_time": 267568.0,
      "text": "are doing their best to doing their best"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 267568.0,
      "end_time": 268596.0,
      "text": "to put a stop to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 268596.0,
      "end_time": 270230.0,
      "text": "And, if you take some of these steps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 270230.0,
      "end_time": 272317.0,
      "text": "you'll be able to start reducing the annoyance."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 272317.0,
      "end_time": 274210.0,
      "text": "Hey, thanks for watching, this is part of our series,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 274210.0,
      "end_time": 276337.0,
      "text": "Work Flow, where we show you how we're using our own tech,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
